    <p class="eden-eyebrow">Hidden Admin</p><h1>Eden Skye Admin Control Plane</h1><div class="eden-admin-hero"><div><h2>AI content creation approval system</h2><p>This hidden page is the storefront-visible control-plane shell for image, video, content, Shopify, and automation approval. It is intentionally not linked in public navigation.</p><div class="eden-page-actions"><a class="eden-button" href="/collections/ladies">Review Ladies</a><a class="eden-button secondary" href="/pages/payment">Payment Gate</a></div></div><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0754/8905/0678/files/eden-approved-ui-mobile-roster.png?v=1781419417" alt="Eden Skye admin approval UI reference"></div><div class="eden-admin-grid"><article><span>Images</span><strong>Approval Gallery</strong><p>Approved source images, replacement slots, manifest status, and creator-ready assets.</p></article><article><span>Video</span><strong>HeyGen / Xyla Queue</strong><p>Draft scripts, model video packets, social reels, and automation-ready clips.</p></article><article><span>Commerce</span><strong>Black Card Gate</strong><p>Payment activation, products, collections, Shopify sync, and protected launch approvals.</p></article><article><span>Automation</span><strong>GPT Pipeline</strong><p>Content generation, social drafts, validation, receipts, and evidence capture.</p></article></div><div class="eden-reference-grid"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0754/8905/0678/files/eden-approved-desktop-home-reference.png?v=1781419565" alt="Approved desktop reference"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0754/8905/0678/files/eden-approved-mobile-full-reference.png?v=1781419576" alt="Approved mobile reference"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0754/8905/0678/files/eden-approved-ui-mobile-home.png?v=1781419405" alt="Approved mobile home reference"></div>
